metadata.name: Iceland is love
metadata.description:
This is the 1th NFT issued as a single, unique edition.

Photo: 5207 x 6500 px 

The most amazing thing about Iceland is not the lava fields, the hot springs or the glaciers. It is the fact that there is 13,000 km of roads that will take you into this uncharted wilderness.

I still donâ€™t know why, exactly, but I do think people can have a spiritual connection to the landscape, and I certainly did in Iceland.
